  <userestrict id="aspace_46497dc985f1debaf02c772cb204d672">
    <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
<p>Rights to unpublished material produced by individuals, including correspondence, are held for the life of the author +70 years. Unpublished material produced by the Brooklyn Society of Artists will enter the public domain in 120 years from the date of creation. Published material, such as programs and advertisments, are in the public domain.</p>  </userestrict>
